      <img src="/static9/us/2024/08/14/dutch-beach-volleyball-player-convicted-of-rape-says-he-considered-quitting-the-olympics.webp" alt="Dutch beach volleyball player convicted of rape says he considered quitting the Olympics"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Dutch beach volleyball player convicted of rape says he considered quitting the Olympics</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Asked Tuesday in an interview with Dutch national broadcaster NOS if he thought about quitting, Van de Velde said that he considered it both before and during the Olympics, but he ultimately decided to compete.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/08/14/dutch-beach-volleyball-player-convicted-of-rape-says-he-considered-quitting-the-olympics/"  >(The Associated Press, WFLA, NBC)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Tue, 13 Aug 2024 20:00:08 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Tue, 13 Aug 2024 20:00:08 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="The Associated Press, WFLA, NBC">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/us/2024/08/13/news-outlets-were-leaked-insider-material-from-the-trump-campaign-they-chose-not-to-print-it.webp" alt="News outlets were leaked insider material from the Trump campaign. They chose not to print it"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">News outlets were leaked insider material from the Trump campaign. They chose not to print it</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      At least three news outlets were leaked confidential material from inside the Donald Trump campaign, including its report vetting JD Vance as a vice presidential candidate. So far, each has refused to reveal any details about what they received.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/08/13/news-outlets-were-leaked-insider-material-from-the-trump-campaign-they-chose-not-to-print-it/"  >(The Associated Press, WFLA, NBC)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div></div><div class="column vcwi"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Tue, 13 Aug 2024 16:49:55 +0000">
