           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" >
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Senators launch probe into Kroger over alleged surge pricing</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      They're concerned the grocery chain might be using technology to raise prices when shopping is at its busiest.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/08/13/senators-launch-probe-into-kroger-over-alleged-surge-pricing/"  >(Kelsey Kernstine, WGN 9)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div></div><div class="column text"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
