           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Millions of kids still skip school. Could the answer be recess &#8212; and a little cash?</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      MEDFORD, Mass. (AP) — Flerentin “Flex” Jean-Baptiste missed so much school he had to repeat his freshman year at Medford High outside Boston. At school, “you do the same thing every day,” said Jean-Baptiste, who was absent 30 days his first year. “That gets very frustrating.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/08/15/millions-of-kids-still-skip-school-could-the-answer-be-recess-and-cash/"  >(The Associated Press, KRON4)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Tue, 13 Aug 2024 16:36:35 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Tue, 13 Aug 2024 16:36:35 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Raven Moore, ABC 4">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
