      <img src="/static9/us/2024/08/13/arkansas-police-officer-fired-after-video-shows-him-assaulting-inmate-in-patrol-car.webp" alt="Arkansas police officer fired after video shows him assaulting inmate in patrol car"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Arkansas police officer fired after video shows him assaulting inmate in patrol car</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      A Jonesboro, Arkansas, police officer was terminated after he was caught on video assaulting an inmate handcuffed in the back of his patrol car, the Jonesboro Police Department announced.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/08/13/arkansas-police-officer-fired-after-video-shows-him-assaulting-inmate-in-patrol-car/"  >(Raven Moore, ABC 4)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
