  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/us/2024/08/14/most-women-oppose-leaving-abortion-laws-to-the-states-across-party-lines-poll.webp" alt="Most women oppose leaving abortion laws to the states, across party lines: poll"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Most women oppose leaving abortion laws to the states, across party lines: poll</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Three quarters of reproductive age women in the United States oppose letting states decide whether abortion is legal, including large majorities of Democrats and independents, according to a new survey.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/08/14/most-women-oppose-leaving-abortion-laws-to-the-states-across-party-lines-poll/"  >(Nathaniel Weixel, Fox 5)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
