    <h3 itemprop="headline">After 3 years of Taliban rule, life continues to get worse in Afghanistan</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Life in Afghanistan continues to deteriorate in the years after the Taliban takeover of Kabul and the U.S. withdrawal as women&apos;s right vanish and the humanitarian crisis escalates.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2024/08/15/after-3-years-taliban-rule-life-continues-get-worse-afghanistan/"  >(Fox News)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
