    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">A trainee doctor is raped and killed in India, sparking protests and an attack at a medical college</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      A trainee doctor was raped and killed, sparking protests in several cities and an attack on a medical college campus as doctors and paramedics in several cities across India demand better and safer working conditions.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2024/08/15/a-trainee-doctor-is-raped-and-killed-in-india-sparking-protests-and-an-attack-at-a-medical-college/"  >(Bikas Das, Associated Press, KPRC 2)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
