           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">US Energy Secretary calls for more nuclear power while celebrating $35 billion Georgia reactors</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      WAYNESBORO, Ga. (AP) — U.S. Energy Secretary Jennifer Granholm on Friday called for more nuclear reactors to be built in the United States and worldwide.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/tech/2024/08/15/us-energy-secretary-calls-for-more-nuclear-power-while-celebrating-35-billion-georgia-reactors/"  >(JEFF AMY, Associated Press, Fox 5)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
