    <h3 itemprop="headline">Google rolls out Pixel 9 phones earlier than usual as AI race with Apple heats up</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      MOUNTAIN VIEW, Calif. (AP) — Google on Tuesday unveiled its next generation of Pixel phones, providing the maker of Android software a head start on the next iPhone in the race to bring more artificial-intelligence services to devices that have become people’s constant companions.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/tech/2024/08/13/google-rolls-out-pixel-9-phones-earlier-than-usual-as-ai-race-with-apple-heats-up/"  >(MICHAEL LIEDTKE, Associated Press, NewsNation)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
