    <h3 itemprop="headline">Hackers may have stolen every Americans' Social Security number: Report</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      The theft happened in April, according to a class-action lawsuit filed in federal court in Fort Lauderdale, Florida.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/tech/2024/08/15/hackers-identify-theft-social-security-usdod/"  >(Rich Johnson, The Hill)</a>
