    <h3 itemprop="headline">Harbaugh says Kaepernick will not be a player or coach with the Chargers this season</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      EL SEGUNDO, Calif. (AP) — If Colin Kaepernick wants to join the Los Angeles Chargers, it will not be until next year at the earliest. And it will only be as a member of Jim Harbaugh's coaching staff.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/sports/2024/08/16/harbaugh-says-kaepernick-will-not-be-a-player-or-coach-with-the-chargers-this-season/"  >(JOE REEDY, Associated Press, KGET 17, NBC)</a>
