    <h3 itemprop="headline">Hoyer experienced &#8216;mild&#8217; stroke, has &#8216;no lingering symptoms,&#8217; office says</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Rep. Steny Hoyer (D-Md.) experienced a “mild” stroke Sunday night and, after treatment, is not experiencing lingering symptoms, the congressman’s office announced Tuesday.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2024/08/14/hoyer-experienced-mild-stroke-has-no-lingering-symptoms-office-says/"  >(Mychael Schnell, NewsNation)</a>
