    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">RFK Jr. asked Harris for Cabinet post in exchange for dropping out, endorsing her: report</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Independent presidential candidate Robert F. Kennedy Jr. attempted to meet with Vice President Kamala Harris to discuss the possibility of serving in her administration.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2024/08/15/rfk-asked-harris-cabinet-post-exchange-dropping-out-endorsing-her-report/"  >(Fox News)</a>
    </p>
