      <img src="/static9/politics/2024/08/16/why-the-progressive-squad-is-getting-smaller-after-defeats-this-primary-cycle.webp" alt="Why the progressive 'Squad' is getting smaller after defeats this primary cycle"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Why the progressive 'Squad' is getting smaller after defeats this primary cycle</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      WASHINGTON (AP) — The so-called "Squad” — a group of progressive lawmakers in the House — is set to shrink next year after two members suffered primary defeats this election cycle following an unprecedented deluge of special interest spending. The primary losses for Reps.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2024/08/16/why-the-progressive-squad-is-getting-smaller-after-defeats-this-primary-cycle/"  >(FARNOUSH AMIRI and ANTHONY IZAGUIRRE, Associated Press, KGET 17, NBC)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
