    <h3 itemprop="headline">Harris zeroes in on high food and housing prices as inflation plays a big role in the campaign</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Vice President Kamala Harris is zeroing in on high food and housing prices as her campaign previews an economic policy speech coming up in North Carolina.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2024/08/15/harris-is-zeroing-in-on-high-food-prices-as-inflation-remains-a-big-issue-in-the-presidential-race/"  >(Associated Press, Local 4)</a>
