      <img src="/static9/politics/2024/08/15/vance-says-media-acted-like-biden-einstein-aim-make-harris-second-coming-abraham-lincoln.webp" alt="Vance says media acted like Biden was 'Einstein,' aim to make Harris into 'second coming of Abraham Lincoln'"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
