    <h3 itemprop="headline">Vance says media acted like Biden was 'Einstein,' aim to make Harris into 'second coming of Abraham Lincoln'</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Republican vice presidential nominee JD Vance accused the media on Thursday of pretending President Biden is &quot;Albert Einstein&quot; and Vice President Kamala Harris is &quot;the second coming of Abraham Lincoln.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2024/08/15/vance-says-media-acted-like-biden-einstein-aim-make-harris-second-coming-abraham-lincoln/"  >(Fox News)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
