  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/politics/2024/08/15/dnc-trying-remove-candidate-from-state-ballot-who-received-more-votes-than-trump-margin-victory-2016.webp" alt="Dems try to block Green Party candidate from presidential ballot in major swing state"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Dems try to block Green Party candidate from presidential ballot in major swing state</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      The Democratic National Committee (DNC) filed a complaint to remove Green Party presidential candidate Jill Stein from the ballot in Wisconsin.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2024/08/15/dnc-trying-remove-candidate-from-state-ballot-who-received-more-votes-than-trump-margin-victory-2016/"  >(Fox News)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div></div><div class="column vcwi"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Tue, 13 Aug 2024 20:57:11 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Tue, 13 Aug 2024 20:57:11 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Anna Kutz, NewsNation">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/politics/2024/08/13/tim-walz-project-2025.webp" alt="What Tim Walz has said about Project 2025"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">What Tim Walz has said about Project 2025</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Walz has continually attacked former President Donald Trump's ties to the nearly 1,000-page document.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2024/08/13/tim-walz-project-2025/"  >(Anna Kutz, NewsNation)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
